HONOR THE TRUTH , caught in tight quarters after bumping with SUPER MONEY leaving the starting gate, hugged the inner rail on the turn, altered course to the two path entering the stretch to avoid the heels of GOLDEN BLOSSOM, moved out in mid stretch and finished willingly. CELTIC WAR CRY circled foes around the turn, was four deep at the head of the stretch, was brushed by SUPER MONEY near the three sixteenths pole then bumped that one near the eighth pole before flattening out. SUPER MONEY bumped with HONOR THE TRUTH at the start, raced in the two path on the turn, brushed CELTIC WAR CRY when drifting out in upper stretch then was bumped by that one near the eighth pole. HEY RIRI , wide on the turn, was outrun. GOLDEN BLOSSOM , steadied in traffic mid way down the backstretch, raced along the inner rail on the turn and faltered. There was a stewards' inquiry concerning the stretch run but no action was taken.

THUNDER BOSS vied two wide on a short lead outside MEETMEATTHEBEACH, shook clear of that one into the turn, met an outside challenge mid turn, stayed on to the inside of runners past mid stretch then faded late. MEETMEATTHEBEACH vied inside THUNDER BOSS early on, steadied when in a bit tight into the turn, regrouped and tracked under rating while saving ground, edged up along the rail in upper stretch, failed to go on past mid stretch and weakened. MATTY BO bobbled outward at the break, recovered and stalked two wide early on, steadied behind MEETMEATTHEBEACH into the turn, shifted three wide to pursue but came up empty in the final furlong. DON DIVA dropped back early and failed to respond.

KINGDOM FORCE brushed with an inner rival at the break, chased two wide, made a slight run past the three eighths, lacked a further response and dropped back in the drive.
